headline: Ashes to Alpha: Why Intuitive Surgical’s (ISRG) Fallout is a Legit Upside Opportunity
summary: With concerns that the Trump administration’s tariffs could impact Intuitive Surgical’s business, ISRG stock tumbled on Wednesday, presenting a contrarian prospect.

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock to Consider Right Now and 2 That Underwhelm
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.
